<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dolomity 2026 - Oficjalny Niezbędnik Wyjazdowy</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts: Inter & Plus Jakarta Sans -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Leaflet CSS for Map -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css" />
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
        }
        .bg-mountain {
            background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506744038136-46273834b3fb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        /* Custom scrollbar styling */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #f1f5f9;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #94a3b8;
        }
        /* Map container styling */
        #map {
            height: 450px;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            z-index: 10;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-800 antialiased selection:bg-emerald-500 selection:text-white">

    <!-- Hero / Header Section -->
    <header class="bg-mountain text-white py-16 px-4 md:py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[radial-gradient(#fff_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px]"></div>
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-300 border border-emerald-500/30 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 animate-pulse">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-mountain-sun"></i> Alpejska Przygoda 2026
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 drop-shadow-sm">
                Kierunek: <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Dolomity</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light mb-8">
                Interaktywny przewodnik, harmonogram i niezbędnik dla całej ekipy. Rower, trekking, piękne jeziora i relaks dostosowany do dzieciaków!
            </p>

            <!-- Countdown Timer -->
            <div class="bg-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-md inline-grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl max-w-lg mx-auto w-full">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <span id="days" class="block text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-400">00</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-medium">Dni</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center border-l border-white/10">
                    <span id="hours" class="block text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-400">00</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-medium">Godziny</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center border-l border-white/10">
                    <span id="minutes" class="block text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-400">00</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-medium">Minuty</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center border-l border-white/10">
                    <span id="seconds" class="block text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-400">00</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-medium">Sekundy</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Navigation Quick-Links & Global Config -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 -mt-8 relative z-20">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl p-4 md:p-6 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 border border-slate-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-day text-lg"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block font-medium">Termin startu</span>
                    <input type="date" id="tripStartDate" value="2026-07-15" class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 bg-transparent border-none p-0 focus:ring-0 cursor-pointer" onchange="updateTripDates()">
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-55 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 bg-blue-50">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-users text-lg"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block font-medium">Ekipa</span>
                    <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Dorośli + Dzieci</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-sun text-lg"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block font-medium">Pogoda</span>
                    <a href="https://www.bergfex.com/it/suedtirol/wetter/" target="_blank" class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-600 hover:underline flex items-center gap-1">
                        Sprawdź Dolomity <i class="fa-solid fa-up-right-from-square text-[10px]"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-55 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 bg-red-50">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-house-medical text-lg"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block font-medium">Numer alarmowy</span>
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-red-600">112 (oraz 118 górskie)</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content Grid -->
    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Left Side: Interactive Map & Essential Widgets -->
        <section class="lg:col-span-5 order-2 lg:order-1 space-y-8">
            
            <!-- Map Card -->
            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 space-y-4">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot text-emerald-500"></i> Mapa Naszych Przygód
                    </h2>
                    <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 py-1 px-2.5 rounded-full font-medium">Kliknij dzień, by przybliżyć</span>
                </div>
                <div id="map"></div>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 italic text-center">
                    Kliknij na piny na mapie, aby zobaczyć przypisany dzień wyjazdu i szczegóły.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Motivational Corner for Kids -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-orange-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-amber-100 space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-3xl">🏆</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-950 text-base">Strefa Młodego Odkrywcy</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-amber-700">Zadania i nagrody za odwagę i uśmiech na szlaku!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="space-y-3 pt-2">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4 p-3 bg-white/80 rounded-xl border border-amber-200/50">
                        <div class="flex gap-2.5">
                            <span class="text-xl">🎒</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-800">Mały Pomocnik (Codziennie)</h4>
                                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Spakowanie własnego małego plecaczka na wycieczkę.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-xs bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">10 pkt</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4 p-3 bg-white/80 rounded-xl border border-amber-200/50">
                        <div class="flex gap-2.5">
                            <span class="text-xl">⏰</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-800">Poranny Ninja (Dzień 8)</h4>
                                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Wstanie bez marudzenia przed 7:00 na Lago di Sorapis!</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-xs bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">50 pkt</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4 p-3 bg-white/80 rounded-xl border border-amber-200/50">
                        <div class="flex gap-2.5">
                            <span class="text-xl">🥾</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-800">Zdobywca Secedy (Dzień 6)</h4>
                                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Zrobienie pętli i uśmiechnięta fotka z widokiem na iglice.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-xs bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">30 pkt</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-amber-600/10 p-3 rounded-xl border border-amber-600/20 text-center">
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold text-amber-900">🎁 Główna Nagroda dla Dzieciaków:</p>
                    <p class="text-[11px] text-amber-800 mt-1">Giga puchar lodowy w Cortina d'Ampezzo (Dzień 9) oraz miano "Dolomitowego Wojownika"!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Essential Guidelines & Safety -->
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 space-y-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation text-amber-500"></i> Ważne Zasady Wyjazdowe
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-xs text-slate-600">
                    <li class="flex gap-2">
                        <span class="text-emerald-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></span>
                        <span><strong>Tempo dostosowane do najsłabszych:</strong> Pamiętamy o dzieciach! Odpuszczamy, gdy brakuje sił. Góry poczekają.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2">
                        <span class="text-emerald-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></span>
                        <span><strong>Warunki pogodowe:</strong> Plany mogą ulec zmianie w przypadku ulewy lub burzy (szczególnie Tre Cime i Sorapis).</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2">
                        <span class="text-emerald-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></span>
                        <span><strong>Gotówka:</strong> Warto mieć euro w gotówce (np. wstęp na stawy w Dobbiaco 5€/osoba, schroniska, parkingi).</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2">
                        <span class="text-emerald-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></span>
                        <span><strong>Rower:</strong> Obowiązkowe kaski dla każdego, zwłaszcza na zjazdach z Lago di Braies i trasie do Cortiny.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </section>

        <!-- Right Side: Beautiful Interactive Itinerary Timeline -->
        <section class="lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-6">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Harmonogram Dzień po Dniu</h2>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Klikaj karty, by podświetlić trasę na mapie</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Filter Badges -->
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <button onclick="filterDays('all')" class="filter-btn active text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-900 text-white transition-all">Wszystko</button>
                    <button onclick="filterDays('hike')" class="filter-btn text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white text-slate-600 border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all">🥾 Trekking</button>
                    <button onclick="filterDays('bike')" class="filter-btn text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white text-slate-600 border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all">🚲 Rower</button>
                    <button onclick="filterDays('relax')" class="filter-btn text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white text-slate-600 border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all">⛱️ Relaks</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day Timeline -->
            <div class="space-y-6 relative before:absolute before:inset-0 before:right-auto before:left-4 md:before:left-6 before:w-0.5 before:bg-slate-200 before:content-['']">
                
                <!-- Dzień 1 -->
                <div class="day-card relative pl-12 md:pl-16 transition-all duration-300" data-type="relax" id="day-1-anchor">
                    <div onclick="focusMap(46.7329, 12.2798, 12, 1)" class="cursor-pointer group bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col gap-4 relative transition-all hover:shadow-md">
                        <!-- Left Dot -->
                        <span class="absolute left-[-32px] md:left-[-46px] top-6 w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-200 border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-bold z-10 group-hover:bg-slate-900 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">1</span>
                        
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-start gap-2">
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-wider uppercase dynamic-day-name" data-day-offset="0">Dzień 1</span>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors">Przyjazd i Zakwaterowanie</h3>
                            </div>
                            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-slate-100 text-slate-700">Relaks / Integracja</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Przyjazd na miejsce, rozpakowanie bagaży, ogarnięcie przestrzeni mieszkalnej i wspólny wieczór zapoznawczo-planistyczny przy lokalnym włoskim winie lub piwie.
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-100 pt-3">
                            <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-hotel"></i> Zakwaterowanie</span>
                            <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-beer-mug-empty"></i> Luźny wieczór</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Dzień 2 -->
                <div class="day-card relative pl-12 md:pl-16 transition-all duration-300" data-type="bike" id="day-2-anchor">
                    <div onclick="focusMap(46.6943, 12.0847, 13, 2)" class="cursor-pointer group bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col gap-4 relative transition-all hover:shadow-md">
                        <span class="absolute left-[-32px] md:left-[-46px] top-6 w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-200 border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-bold z-10 group-hover:bg-slate-900 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">2</span>
                        
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-start gap-2">
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-wider uppercase dynamic-day-name" data-day-offset="1">Dzień 2</span>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors">Lago di Braies Rowerem & Festiwal</h3>
                            </div>
                            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700">Trasa Rowerowa + Spacer</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Ruszamy rowerami nad jedno z najpiękniejszych jezior Dolomitów – <strong>Lago di Braies (21 km)</strong>. Na miejscu opcja wynajęcia uroczej drewnianej łódki lub spokojny spacer wokół jeziora (ok. 2h, na tyle ile starczy sił). 
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-indigo-50/50 p-3 rounded-xl border border-indigo-100 text-xs text-indigo-900">
                            <strong>Wieczorna atrakcja:</strong> Od 17:30 do 22:00 ruszamy na lokalny festiwal w miasteczku – <strong>Dolomythos Summer Fest</strong>! Lokalne jedzenie, muzyka i świetny klimat.
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-100 pt-3">
                            <span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-emerald-600 font-medium"><i class="fa-solid fa-bicycle"></i> 21 km</span>
                            <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-person-hiking"></i> 2h wokół jeziora</span>
                            <span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-indigo-600 font-medium"><i class="fa-solid fa-champagne-glasses"></i> Dolomythos Fest</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Dzień 3 -->
                <div class="day-card relative pl-12 md:pl-16 transition-all duration-300" data-type="hike" id="day-3-anchor">
                    <div onclick="focusMap(46.6125, 12.2952, 13, 3)" class="cursor-pointer group bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col gap-4 relative transition-all hover:shadow-md">
                        <span class="absolute left-[-32px] md:left-[-46px] top-6 w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-200 border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-bold z-10 group-hover:bg-slate-900 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">3</span>
                        
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-start gap-2">
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-wider uppercase dynamic-day-name" data-day-offset="2">Dzień 3</span>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors">Tre Cime & Cadini di Misurina</h3>
                            </div>
                            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-50 text-amber-700">Średni / Trudny Hike</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Ikona Dolomitów! Długi, malowniczy trekking wokół <strong>Tre Cime di Lavaredo (ok. 10 km)</strong>. Dodatkowo podejdziemy na widowiskowy punkt widokowy <strong>Cadini di Misurina</strong> (krótki odcinek, ok. 30-45 minut). Po trekkingu zjeżdżamy do klimatycznego miasteczka Misurina nad jeziorem na zasłużony obiad.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-amber-50 p-3 rounded-xl border border-amber-200 text-xs text-amber-900">
                            🚨 <strong>Opcja awaryjna dla zmęczonych (Ika, Adam, Judi):</strong> W razie ubytku sił na Tre Cime, spokojny relaks nad jeziorem Misurina zamiast pełnej pętli.
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-100 pt-3">
                            <span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-amber-700 font-medium"><i class="fa-solid fa-shoe-prints"></i> 10 km trekking</span>
                            <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i> Łącznie ok. 4-5h</span>
                            <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-utensils"></i> Obiad w Misurina</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Dzień 4 i 5 -->
                <div class="day-card relative pl-12 md:pl-16 transition-all duration-300" data-type="bike" id="day-4-anchor">
                    <div onclick="focusMap(46.7231, 12.2183, 12, 4)" class="cursor-pointer group bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 p-5 md:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col gap-4 relative transition-all hover:shadow-md">
                        <span class="absolute left-[-32px] md:left-[-46px] top-6 w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-200 border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-bold z-10 group-hover:bg-slate-900 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">4+5</span>
                        
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-start gap-2">
                            <div>
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-wider uppercase dynamic-day-name" data-day-offset="3">Weekend</span>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors">Lago di Dobbiaco, Prato Piazza lub Lienz</h3>
                            </div>
                            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700">Elastyczny Weekend</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Weekend pełen opcji! Wycieczka rowerowa nad malownicze <strong>Lago di Dobbiaco</strong>, piknik, relaksik i krótki spacer wokół (ok. 45 min). Popołudniu możemy podskoczyć na zielone łąki <strong>Prato Piazza</strong> (wjazd autem możliwy po 16:00 z Ponticello, łagodny trekking do schroniska, mało turystycznie i spokojnie).
